reviewText:
This is actually a CD, not a DVD, published by Coach Training Alliance. The sections are:
Introduction 2m1s
The Art of Coaching 14m59s
Seizing the Coachable Moment 22m56s
Inviting the Shift 12m32s
Framing the Masterpiece 15m29s
Review 10m06

The CD case is labeled Masterful Coaching Skills and the CD itself is labeled Mastering Coaching Skills.
